<div class='span12'>
<h2>Die Sprache(n) der Comics (Sammelband)</h2>
<h3>Kolloquium in Heidelberg, 16.-17. Juni 2009</h3>
<hr>
<abbr class='unapi-id' title='1232'></abbr>
<div class='row-fluid'>
<div class='span8'>
<h3>Allgemeine Angaben</h3>
